rows.label: xs10090100_MSG0004
rows.name:
Ganglion learn hard way what happens
when you mess with Team Tatsu![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs10090100_MSG0005
rows.name: We fought as a team and we fought well.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs10090100_MSG0006
rows.name: I only hope there aren't any more like this back at their base...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs10090100_MSG0007
rows.name:
If these things hit the city in numbers,
we'd have no chance at all.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs10090100_MSG0009
rows.name:
Exactly another reason we need to find
that Lifehold Core as soon as possible.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs10090100_MSG0011
rows.name:
Remember what the Wrothian prince told us in Sylvalum?
About the Ganglion?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs10090100_MSG0013
rows.name: I don't know why that is...but it might be the key to victory.[ST:wait ]
